---
title: Mild Thai Pumpkin & Veggie Curry with Jasmine Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: This Thai red curry is loaded with veggies, giving it plenty of nutritional virtue to boast about. With pumpkin, carrot and baby spinach coated in a creamy red curry sauce, they become soft, sweet and incredibly moreish for an all-round wholesome dinner.

*Unfortunately, this week's Asian greens were in short supply, so we've replaced them with baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-yellow-pumpkin-curry-f837147a.jpg
